data.description: Welcome home to this spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bath retreat in Greenbriar. The house beckons with great views and a beautiful backyard, creating an irresistible allure. Inside, an open floor plan and vaulted ceilings enhance the sense of space and airiness. The kitchen boasts stainless appliances, and two rooms offer glimpses of Longs Peak and Meeker Mountain. With a newer roof, updated appliances, and central HVAC, this residence seamlessly combines modern comfort with a touch of nature's beauty. Act quickly - this gem won't be on the market for long!
